snippet.title: Dark Castle (Dos game 1987)
snippet.description:
Dark Castle was a very famous classic platform game released for many platforms such as Apple Mac (1986), Commodore 64 (1987), Amiga (1987), Atari ST (1987), Apple IIGS (1989), Sega Genesis (1991), Philips CD-i (1992), MSX (1993).
This version is remade with EGA graphics.

You can kill enemy units using a rock.
If you fall out of heights, you get damaged.
To me, it's so difficult.
